Name: ManagedRepresentationReference
Description: Substitution group head for referencing Managed Representations. For example, ManagedTextRepresentationReference, ManagedNumericRepresentationReference, etc.

Name: CategorySchemeReference
Description: A reference to a CategoryScheme as the managed component of a representation.

Name: CodeListReference
Description: A reference to a CodeList as the managed component of a representation.

Name: CodeSubsetInformation
Description: Allows further specification of the codes to use from the CodeList.

Name: IncludedGeographicStructureCodes
Description: Identifies the Geographic Structure codes included by the Authorized source of the code, the geographic location being used and the locations to exclude.

Name: IncludedGeographicLocationCodes
Description: Identifies the Geographic Location codes included by the Authorized source of the code, the geographic location being used and the locations to exclude.
